data.description: Look no further here is the perfect townhouse in Quail Valley near the golf course!!    This lovely townhome offers an open layout and feature two living rooms one with a cozy fireplace, a formal dining room perfect for family dinners or maybe used as a home office space instead. All 3 bedrooms are upstairs and are very spacious. The back patio is perfect for grilling and have space for gardening.     This home is a must see, schedule your private tour today!
